title: Matryoshka Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Thai, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Russian, Ukranian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Food is cooked to order. Here you can get steamed cabbage, potatoes, salads, and other dishes as vegetarian by request. Possible to order Ukrainian "varenikis" without eggs in flour with potato and cabbage stuffing. Accepts advance phone orders.
